hydna-cc

Emanuel Dahlberg

http://github.com/EmanueI
===================================================================


compile lib
-------------------------------------------------------------------
To compile the lib:

cd src
make clean
make

A file named libhydna.so, should be created in lib/.


The lib can also be compiled into debug-mode with:

cd src
make debug

Information about packets and redirects will be put on stdout.



compile example
-------------------------------------------------------------------
To compile the example:

cd examples
make clean
make


run example
-------------------------------------------------------------------
To run the example:

cd examples
./hydnatestclient receive


And in another shell

cd examples
./hydnatestclient send


This assumes that you have a tcpbin gate running on your
local machine on the port 7120.



info
-------------------------------------------------------------------
All the headers can be found in include/ with comments.

Look in the Makefile in examples/ to find out how to link the lib.

